            "body": "Already fixed on master by cf9ad39267 (#40073). It adds a `decoded.id == vim.NIL` check right before the `_assert_integer` call, so a null-id response is logged and ignored instead of crashing. I verified the crash is gone with that patch applied on v0.12.1. Closing.",
